data.description: Welcome to your dream retreat in the heart of Sonoma! This 2-bedroom condo in the sought-after Sonoma Greens community offers a perfect blend of luxury and leisure. Nestled amidst the scenic beauty of Sonoma, this residence is a stone's throw away from the pristine golf course, promising stunning views and a tranquil ambiance.    Step into the spacious and tastefully designed condo, where natural light floods through large windows, highlighting the modern yet cozy living spaces. The two bedrooms provide a serene escape, each offering comfort and style.    Beyond the walls of your private haven, immerse yourself in the community's amenities. Lounge by the inviting swimming pool, perfect for unwinding on warm Sonoma afternoons. Challenge your friends to a friendly match on the tennis courts, surrounded by lush greenery. Whether you're a golf enthusiast or simply appreciate the beauty of the outdoors, this condo caters to your every need.
